<subSubSection lastPageId="42" lastPageNumber="43" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="41.[151,1437,1410,1756]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,361,1570,1596]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Distribution:</emphasis>
From Sonora province in the Continental Nearctic dominion of the North American Pacific subregion of the Nearctic region to Napo, 
<collectingCountry box="[648,739,1610,1636]" name="Guyana" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Guyana</collectingCountry>
and Roraima provinces of the Amazonian subregion of the Neotropical region.
</paragraph>
